                   <persName ref="PRS8666Sebestya"><roleName type="title">marǝd ʾazmāč</roleName> </persName> of <placeName ref="LOC5597Sawa">
                  Šawā </placeName>who succeeded his father <persName ref="PRS7467NagasiK">Nagāśi Krǝstos Warada Qāl</persName>. 
