                     Šawā </placeName> from there.  Unlike his father, <persName ref="PRS8666Sebestya">Sǝbǝstyānos</persName> never sought the recognition 
                  of the emeperors at <placeName ref="LOC3577Gondar">Gondar</placeName>. 
